SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[EndTime] < GETDATE())

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Problems] AS [e1]
    WHERE ([e1].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[Id] = [e1].[LessonId])
) AS [ProblemsCount], [e].[Type]
FROM [Lessons] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]

FROM [Contests] AS [e.Contests]

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e2]
    LEFT JOIN (

        WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
    ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

) AS [t1] ON [e.Contests].[LessonId] = [t1].[Id]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)

    WHERE [e].[Id] = [e1].[SubmissionId]
) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)

SELECT [e].[CourseId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[Name], [t].[Id] AS [PracticeId], (
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Problems] AS [e1]
    WHERE ([e1].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[Id] = [e1].[LessonId])
) AS [ProblemsCount], [e].[Type]
FROM [Lessons] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[CourseId] = @__courseId_0)
ORDER BY [e].[Id]
2021-12-21 11:26:44.584 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[@__courseId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']

FROM [Contests] AS [e.Contests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e2].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e2]
    LEFT JOIN (
        SELECT [e3].*
        FROM [Practices] AS [e3]
        WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
    ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [Problems] AS [e1]
    WHERE ([e1].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[Id] = [e1].[LessonId])

    SELECT [e0].*

    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]

FROM [Contests] AS [e.Contests]

    FROM [Lessons] AS [e2]

SELECT TOP(1) [e].[CourseId], [e].[Id] AS [Id0], [e].[LessonPassword], [e].[Name], [t].[Id] AS [PracticeId]
FROM [Lessons] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[Id] = @__id_0)
ORDER BY [e].[Id]

INNER JOIN (
    SELECT TOP(1) [e1].[Id]
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e1]

        SELECT [e2].*
        FROM [Practices] AS [e2]
        WHERE [e2].[IsDeleted] = 0

WHERE [e.Problems].[IsDeleted] = 0
ORDER BY [t1].[Id]

FROM [Submissions] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)

) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY [e].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e].[Id]

2021-12-21 11:30:35.971 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (7ms) [Parameters=[], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

        WHERE ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND (([e].[ClassNumber] = @__classNumber_0) AND ([e].[ClassType] = @__classType_1)))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END

SELECT [e].[EndTime], [e].[LessonId], [t0].[Id] AS [LessonPracticeId], [e].[Name]
FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)

    WHEN [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)

    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0

    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)

FROM [Contests] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Lessons] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[LessonId] = [t].[Id]

    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [t].[Id] = [t0].[LessonId]

SELECT TOP(1) CASE
    WHEN ([t0].[SubmissionType] = 2) OR [e].[Code] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [e].[Code], CASE
    WHEN [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [e].[CompilationErrors], [e].[Id], [t0].[Name] AS [ProblemName], [t0].[SubmissionType] AS [ProblemSubmissionType], [e].[SubmisionDate], [t].[UserName] AS [UserUsername]
FROM [Submissions] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[UserId] = [t].[Id]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e1].*
    FROM [Problems] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e1].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t0] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[Id] = @__id_0)

SELECT TOP(1) CASE
    WHEN ([t0].[SubmissionType] = 2) OR [e].[Code] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [e].[Code], CASE
    WHEN [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NULL
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END, [e].[CompilationErrors], [e].[Id], [t0].[Name] AS [ProblemName], [t0].[SubmissionType] AS [ProblemSubmissionType], [e].[SubmisionDate], [t].[UserName] AS [UserUsername]
FROM [Submissions] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [AspNetUsers] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0

    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e].[Id] = [e1].[SubmissionId]
) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY [e].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e].[Id]

SELECT CASE
    WHEN EXISTS (
        SELECT 1
        FROM [Lessons] AS [e]
        WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[Id] = @__id_0))
    THEN CAST(1 AS BIT) ELSE CAST(0 AS BIT)
END
2021-12-21 14:56:22.307 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (4ms) [Parameters=[@__lessonId_0='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT TOP(1) [t].[Id]
FROM [Lessons] AS [e]
LEFT JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].*
    FROM [Practices] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[Id] = [t].[LessonId]
WHERE (([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND ([e].[Id] = @__lessonId_0)

        FROM [Submissions] AS [e3]
        INNER JOIN (

            FROM [Problems] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e4].[IsDeleted] = 0

        WHERE (([e3].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND (([e3].[UserId] = @__userId_0) AND ([t1].[IsExtraTask] = 0))) AND ([t].[Id] = [e3].[ContestId])
        GROUP BY [e3].[ProblemId]
    ) AS [t2]

    SELECT SUM([e5].[MaxPoints])
    FROM [Problems] AS [e5]
    WHERE (([e5].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e5].[IsExtraTask] = 0)) AND ([t0].[Id] = [e5].[LessonId])

SELECT [e].[Id], [e].[ActualPoints], [e].[Code], [e].[CompilationErrors], [e].[ContestId], [e].[CreatedOn], [e].[DeletedOn], [e].[IsDeleted], [e].[ModifiedOn], [e].[PracticeId], [e].[ProblemId], [e].[SubmisionDate], [e].[UserId], [t].[Id], [t].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [t].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [t].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [t].[AutomatedTestingProject], [t].[CreatedOn], [t].[DeletedOn], [t].[IsDeleted], [t].[IsExtraTask], [t].[LessonId], [t].[MaxPoints], [t].[ModifiedOn], [t].[Name], [t].[OrderBy], [t].[SubmissionType], [t].[TestingStrategy], [t].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
FROM [Submissions] AS [e]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT [e0].[Id], [e0].[AllowedMemoryInMegaBytes], [e0].[AllowedMinCodeDifferenceInPercentage], [e0].[AllowedTimeInMilliseconds], [e0].[AutomatedTestingProject], [e0].[CreatedOn], [e0].[DeletedOn], [e0].[IsDeleted], [e0].[IsExtraTask], [e0].[LessonId], [e0].[MaxPoints], [e0].[ModifiedOn], [e0].[Name], [e0].[OrderBy], [e0].[SubmissionType], [e0].[TestingStrategy], [e0].[TimeIntervalBetweenSubmissionInSeconds]
    FROM [Problems] AS [e0]
    WHERE [e0].[IsDeleted] = 0
) AS [t] ON [e].[ProblemId] = [t].[Id]
WHERE ((([e].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
    SELECT COUNT(*)
    FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e1]
    WHERE [e].[Id] = [e1].[SubmissionId]
) > 0) OR [e].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
ORDER BY [e].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e].[Id]
OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
2021-12-21 16:07:07.320 +02:00 [INF] Executed DbCommand (21ms) [Parameters=[@__problemId_0='?' (DbType = Int32), @__userId_1='?' (Size = 450), @__p_2='?' (DbType = Int32), @__p_3='?' (DbType = Int32)], CommandType='"Text"', CommandTimeout='30']
SELECT [x.ExecutedTests].[Id], [x.ExecutedTests].[CreatedOn], [x.ExecutedTests].[Error], [x.ExecutedTests].[ExecutionResultType], [x.ExecutedTests].[IsCorrect], [x.ExecutedTests].[MemoryUsed], [x.ExecutedTests].[ModifiedOn], [x.ExecutedTests].[Output], [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId], [x.ExecutedTests].[TestId], [x.ExecutedTests].[TimeUsed]
FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [x.ExecutedTests]
INNER JOIN (
    SELECT DISTINCT [t1].*
    FROM (
        SELECT [e2].[Id], [e2].[SubmisionDate]
        FROM [Submissions] AS [e2]
        INNER JOIN (
            SELECT [e3].*
            FROM [Problems] AS [e3]
            WHERE [e3].[IsDeleted] = 0
        ) AS [t0] ON [e2].[ProblemId] = [t0].[Id]
        WHERE ((([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0) AND ([e2].[IsDeleted] = 0)) AND (([e2].[ProblemId] = @__problemId_0) AND ([e2].[UserId] = @__userId_1))) AND (((
            SELECT COUNT(*)
            FROM [ExecutedTests] AS [e4]
            WHERE [e2].[Id] = [e4].[SubmissionId]
        ) > 0) OR [e2].[CompilationErrors] IS NOT NULL)
        ORDER BY [e2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [e2].[Id]
        OFFSET @__p_2 ROWS FETCH NEXT @__p_3 ROWS ONLY
    ) AS [t1]
) AS [t2] ON [x.ExecutedTests].[SubmissionId] = [t2].[Id]
ORDER BY [t2].[SubmisionDate] DESC, [t2].[Id]
